text: Grevillea stenogyne is a shrub of the genus Grevillea native to an area in Western Australia. ==See also== * List of Grevillea species ==References== stenogyne Category:Endemic flora of Western Australia Category:Eudicots of Western Australia Category:Proteales of Australia Category:Taxa named by George Bentham Category:Taxa named by Robert Owen Makinson
